====Usage notes====
While most forms of the verb {{m|en|clepe}} are obsolete, ''yclept'' is still occasionally used as an adjective or verb for humorous or archaic effect; as in the set phrase ''aptly yclept''.
====Alternative forms====
* {{l|en|ycleped}}
